# Weather App
A simple web app that lets you check the current weather of any city in Morocco.

## what it does 

  - search for a city name
  - get real-time weather information
  - Shows:
    - temperature
    - weather description
    - weather icon

All data comes from the OpenWeather API.


## how to use it 
  - open the app in Browser
  - type a city name ( Casablanca, Khouribga, Rabat..)
  - click on search button
  - see the current weather instantly

## technologies i used
  - HTML
  - CSS 
  - JavaScript
  - OpenWeather API

## NOTES
 - The app is currently focused on cities in Morocco 
 - Make sure you have Internet to fetch weather data
 - Enter your own OpenWeather API key

---

Made with curiosity and learning in mind :D